```

In this configuration, any import from `svelte-headless-table/*` will be resolved to the corresponding path under `node_modules/svelte-headless-table/lib/*`. This approach is usually not necessary for most libraries, but it can be useful in cases where TypeScript has trouble resolving module paths. 

